              "items": [
                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3vt1h90n/manifest/annotation/p4",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>I must give you Credit for the very able<lb/> note you appended to the article\n                &amp;<lb/> I can assure you that all the <add>Hebrew</add><lb/> here were pleased\n                with it in the<lb/> hope that we may be <add>Hebrew</add></p>\n            <p rend=\"align(center)\">\n                <add>Hebrew</add>\n            </p>\n            <p>some people here think that we should not<lb/> publish such matters as it brings us\n                into<lb/> disrepute before the world and exposes<lb/> our religion to ridicule, they\n                say better let<lb/> us chose between the two evils, and they<lb/> think that the\n                    “<hi rend=\"underline\">wrong doings</hi>” is the lesser<lb/> evil. I tell them\n                plainly I differ from<lb/> them entirely upon the principle</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(center)\">“<add>Hebrew</add>”</p>\n            <p>and I feel assured that you think with<lb/> me in this respect and I should be\n                pleased<lb/> if you think well of it to publish your<lb/> sentiments on the subject\n                I will keep<lb/> you posted on all matters of any interest<lb/> Both congregations\n                were well attended in<lb/>\n                <add>Hebrew</add>. I am told that <persName>Dr Cohn</persName> delivered a<lb/> very\n                impressive sermon in confirming a<lb/> number of Boys and Girls upon the new\n                System<lb/> in the Reform World. My sermon I will send<lb/> you and judge for\n                yourself my folks were very much<lb/> pleased. We had a Boy <add>Hebrew</add> on the\n                        <date>2<hi rend=\"sup\">nd</hi></date> day of</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3vt1h90n/canvas/p4"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
