                    "value": "<p>powerful influence with the congregation<lb/> in general when they see the\n                President<lb/> setting the good example the old adage<lb/> “<add>Hebrew</add>”<lb/>\n                The charitable Institutions among us<lb/> are flourishing and do much good<lb/> the\n                people are certainly ready at all times<lb/> to dispense charity and that too\n                liberally.<lb/> I believe now my dear sir I have<lb/> exhausted all my sources of\n                information<lb/> and I hope I have not exhausted<lb/> your patience to read my long\n                epistle<lb/> but I suppose you are like me at<lb/> times glad to get something fresh\n                from<lb/> abroad however trifling</p>\n            <p>I leave you now in the hope that<lb/> this will reach you in health of mind<lb/> and\n                Body and expect to hear from<lb/> you soon</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">Believe me</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">Yours truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(8)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">H. A. Henry</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
